    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This appears to be a known bug (<a href=\"https://bugs.java.com/bugdatabase/view_bug?bug_id=6430675\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Java bug 6430675: Math.round has surprising behavior for 0x1.fffffffffffffp-2</a>) which has been fixed in Java 7.</p>\n"
  }, {
